---
description: 
globs: *.tsx,*.ts
alwaysApply: false
---
- Don't use React.{anything}. e.g don't use React.ReactElement, use ReactElement instead
- When accessing TEXT_MANAGER, prefer direct access over destructuring to ensure proper type checking
- When using text keys in components, consider creating a dedicated hook if the same text is used in multiple places
- Always mark all interface properties as readonly to enforce immutability
